Factor 1: Critical 16-31. Risk of life threatening harm to self or others.  Significant health problems have developed or will develop.  The user has sensory impairment or will develop health problems such that care or living arrangements will break down or become unsafe without provision of community care services.  Serious abuse or neglect has occurred or will occur. Without the provision of community care services there may be a breakdown of care or living arrangements, or a risk of significant harm, neglect or abuse.